Sentencas: A new generation of nanostructured cathodes for intermediate temperature solid-oxide fuel cells, with very low polarization resistance, is presented.
Titulo: High-performance solid-oxide fuel cell cathodes based on cobaltite nanotubes

Sentencas: They were prepared from cobaltite nanotubes using a fast and simple method that allows the retention of the original nanostructure.
Titulo: High-performance solid-oxide fuel cell cathodes based on cobaltite nanotubes
